This directory contains all the glyph example programs from ivtools, plus
all the glyph example programs from InterViews 3.1:

	bdvtable	bounded-value editing
	examples3.1	sub-directory of InterViews 3.1 examples
	formdemo	value-editing demo
	gclock		glyph clock
	meter		meter example
	radiogroup	radio-buttons
	scrollable	2d scrollable glyph
	scrollfield	scrollable table of field editors
	strchooser	string chooser
	text-editor	emacs-like text editor
	timestamp	editable time glyph

See http://www.ivtools.org/ivtools/glyphs.html for screenshots.
